<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="2Jun1924"><font color="red">2 June 1924</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): This Norweejicker must have been reading my MS surreptitiously, I fear &hellip; it would be well to go into the clinic and have it over &hellip; and &lsquo;my sight is growing thicker on me with the shadows in this place&rsquo;. My memory too is dulled. I cannot remember accurately the first page of Shaun and he is not here to aid me &hellip; The operation &hellip; will be made on Saturday. (7 June 1924) </div>
